/ \u0391\u03a4\u03a1\u039f\u039c\u0397\u03a4\u039f\u03a3 \u0391\u0398\u0397\u039d\u03a9\u039d \u0391\u03a0\u03a3 \u03a0.\u0391.\u0395. / MASSARA CARLOS-ALBERTO|url=http://www.epae.org/player.fds?categ=2&team=22&player=6503&pagecode=04.02.02&langid=1|language=Greek|accessdate=2010-01-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[RSSSF]]|author=Mastrogiannopoulos, Alexander|title=Foreign Players in Greece 1999/00-2001/02|url=http://www.rsssf.com/players/foreign-players-in-grk9902.html|date=2003-06-22}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Massara, Carlos Alberto}}\n[[Category:1978 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Argentine footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:Akratitos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Panelefsiniakos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Marko F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Levadiakos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Asteras Tripoli F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Atromitos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Diagoras F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Superleague Greece players]]\n[[Category:Primera C Metropolitana players]]\n[[Category:Argentine expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Argentine expatriate sportspeople in Greece]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Greece]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Carlos Alberto Massara\n| fullname = Carlos Alberto Massara \n| image = \n| height = {{height|m=1.86}}\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1978|6|19|df=yes}} \n| birth_place =[[Argentina]]\n| currentclub = \n| clubnumber = \n| position = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]]\n| years1 = 1999\u20132001 \n| years2 = 2001\u20132002 \n| years3 = 2002 \n| years4 = 2003\u20132006 \n| years5 = 2007\u20132008 \n| years6 = 2008\u20132010\n| years7 = 2010\u20132011\n| years8 = 2011\n| years9 = 2011\u20132012\n| clubs1 = [[Akratitos F.C.|Akratitos]] \n| clubs2 = [[Panelefsiniakos F.C.|Panelefsiniakos]] \n| clubs3 = [[Marko F.C.|Marko]] \n| clubs4 = [[Levadiakos F.C.|Levadiakos]] \n| clubs5 = [[Asteras Tripoli F.C.|Asteras Tripolis]] \n| clubs6 = [[Atromitos F.C.|Atromitos]]\n| clubs7 = [[Diagoras F.C.|Diagoras]]\n| clubs8 = [[Club Defensores de Salto|Defensores Salto]]\n| clubs9 = [[Defensores de Cambaceres|Defensores Cambaceres]]\n| caps1 = 22  \n| caps2 = \n| caps3 = \n| caps4 = 7  \n| caps5 = 21  \n| caps6 = 29  \n| goals1 = 0  \n| goals2 = \n| goals3 = \n| goals4 = 0  \n| goals5 = 0  \n| goals6 = 2 \n| nationalyears1 = \n| nationalteam1 = \n| nationalcaps1 = \n| nationalgoals1 =\n}}\n  \n'''Carlos Alberto Massara''' (born 19 June 1978) is a [[association football|football]] player.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[Guardian.co.uk]] |title=Stats Centre: Carlos Massara Facts |url=http://guardian.touch-line.com/StatsCentre.asp?CTID=31&CPID=76&TEID=6394&PLID=216998&pStr=Player |accessdate=2010-01-04 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120929181359/http://guardian.touch-line.com/StatsCentre.asp?CTID=31&CPID=76&TEID=6394&PLID=216998&pStr=Player |archivedate=2012-09-29 }}</ref>\n\nMassara moved to Greece to play for [[Akratitos F.C.]] in the [[Alpha Ethniki]] in August 1999.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Hellenic League|title=\u0392 \u0395\u03b8\u03bd\u03b9\u03ba\u03ae / \u0391\u03a4\u03a1\u039f\u039c\u0397\u03a4\u039f\u03a3 \u0391\u0398\u0397\u039d\u03a9\u039d \u0391\u03a0\u03a3 \u03a0.\u0391.\u0395. / MASSARA CARLOS-ALBERTO|url=http://www.epae.org/player.fds?categ=2&team=22&player=6503&pagecode=04.02.02&langid=1|language=Greek|accessdate=2010-01-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[RSSSF]]|author=Mastrogiannopoulos, Alexander|title=Foreign Players in Greece 1999/00-2001/02|url=http://www.rsssf.com/players/foreign-players-in-grk9902.html|date=2003-06-22}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Massara, Carlos Alberto}}\n[[Category:1978 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Argentine footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:Akratitos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Levadiakos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Asteras Tripoli F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Atromitos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Panelefsiniakos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Superleague Greece players]]\n[[Category:Primera C Metropolitana players]]\n[[Category:Argentine expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Argentine expatriate sportspeople in Greece]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Greece]]\n", "name_user": "Geschichte", "label": "safe", "comment": "cats", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carlos_Alberto_Massara"}
